<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="26Sep1933"><font color="red">26 September 1933</font> <i>NLSP</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to Carolus Verhulst of the Servire Press): as I have not heard anything from Mr Pinker I would like to know how things stand with regard to the publication of Mr Joyce&apos;s last fragment. </div>
